{
  "stem": "14613.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in a way, in a way, I would say that if you were to ask me what are my accomplishments, I would say that maybe the most important accomplishment is that we have two children which I consider really good human beings.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that means a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Susan and Jefferey.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we have a couple of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our daughter is married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she's got two children, two girls, by the name of Dara and Eryn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I'm talking to you, she's expecting another one, maybe in September.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was many, many years ago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we changed the name in Atlanta, Georgia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, my records in the Emory University are still under the old name-- Kniker, K-N-I-K-E-R.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what was happening there, particularly for the southerner, this was an extremely difficult name to pronounce, Kniker.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And how do you spell it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how do you pronounce it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Therefore, we decided that somehow for simplicity, both my brother and myself, we changed the name, which is easy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no problem in how to pronounce it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[DRINKS] How did you decide upon the name that you chose?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I imagine, if I were to look at it, there's no reason.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, somebody asked how come Exxon became Exxon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took, I think  I believe, a computer, and they found out the name Exxon, A crazy name like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have any computers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just-- I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just-- like anything, like many things in life, it just happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No rhyme, no reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it's a difficult question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I don't like to talk so much about what I do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I do this, I feel that I should do it without advertising what and how.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
